1. What gave you the edge to be able to put up 8 passing TDs for a new ELF record?

We had our best week of practice last week and it carried over to the game. My O-line and WRs are unbelievable, so that allows me to be able to perform well.

2. What does this impactful win mean for Rhein Fire going forward in the season?

We've had a great start to the season - beating 3 strong conference opponents, but it's a long season. We won't allow early success to distract us from taking things one week at a time.

Back to the books 📚 
I’m excited to officially announce that I’ve enrolled at UWE Bristol in the MBA program. Getting my masters has been a life long dream of mine. The football team here has given me a scholarship to be apart of their football team from now until April, competing in the British University League. Couldn’t be more grateful for this opportunity. Go Bullets🇬🇧

“Let’s raise some money!” MVP of 2023 & @rheinfire’s QB @qbclark is also part of the auction for a good cause 🙏 You can bid for his signed PS5 + Madden NFL 2024 + 2 Controller now & support the @vivaconagua water projects in Uganda. 

📲 Link in Bio!
